OL,5, Campaigners have lost their High Court 
OL,6, battle with the government over its    
OL,7, decision not to implement evacuation   
OL,8, plans for disabled high-rise residents.
OL,10,FCampaign group Claddag wanted it to be 
OL,11,Fa legal requirement for escape plans to
OL,12,Fbe in place for those who might not be 
OL,13,Fable to get out safely in an emergency.
OL,15,FBut a Home Office consultation found   
OL,16,Fthe Grenfell Tower Inquiry's           
OL,17,Frecommendations would be too costly and
OL,18,Fimpractical to implement.              
OL,20,FIt is pursuing an alternative idea.    
